OL,3,CLocation of classic TV comedy
OL,4,Ctransformed into Buddhist peace garden
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FTasha Kacheri was invited along to
OL,8,Fwatch the ceremony.
OL,10,FA peace garden has been completed at a
OL,11,Ffilming location made famous by a long-
OL,12,Frunning TV comedy.
OL,14,FThe Waterloo Hotel in Runcorn,
OL,15,FCheshire, was frequently shown as the
OL,16,Fpub in Two Pints of Lager and a Packet
OL,17,Fof Crisps and is now a Buddhist temple.
