OL,3,CLocation of classic TV comedy
OL,4,Ctransformed into Buddhist peace garden
OL,6,FNow, the transformation of formerly
OL,7,Fderelict land adjoining the building
OL,8,Fhas been completed for people in the
OL,9,Flocal area.
OL,11,FTemple trustee Tony Collacott said:
OL,12,F"The community of Runcorn have been
OL,13,Fvery welcoming to us.
OL,15,F"We wanted to show something in
OL,16,Freturn."
OL,18,FSpecial guests were invited to take
OL,19,Fpart in the topping off ceremony of
OL,20,Fthe garden, which has been designed
OL,21,Ffor a short meditation walk.
