OL,3,CLocation of classic TV comedy
OL,4,Ctransformed into Buddhist peace garden
OL,6,FA six metre-tall bronze statue, one of
OL,7,Fthe biggest of its kind in the UK, is
OL,8,Fthe centrepiece of the garden.
OL,10,FThe Chedi, which enshrines relics and
OL,11,Fkeeps the memory of the Buddha, was
OL,12,Fhandcrafted over eight months by monks
OL,13,Fin Thailand.
OL,15,FThe ceremony saw a Yod Chat placed at
OL,16,Fthe top, which in Buddhism symbolises
OL,17,Fan umbrella casting a protective
OL,18,Fshadow onto the Earth.
