OL,3,CLocation of classic TV comedy
OL,4,Ctransformed into Buddhist peace garden
OL,6,FThe peace garden includes flower beds
OL,7,Fand rockeries and a stone plaque
OL,8,Finviting people to sit and enjoy the
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FBuddhism charity Wat Phra Singh UK
OL,12,Ftook over the pub building in 2013 and
OL,13,Flater received planning permission and
OL,14,Ffunding to create a new hall and peace
OL,15,Fgarden on the adjacent land.
OL,17,FThe project was funded by Reconnecting
OL,18,FRuncorn, which aims regenerate the
OL,19,Flocal area and bring the community
OL,20,Ftogether.
